  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Develop a prospective register assessing the short- and long-term complications of patients
      undergoing interventional rhythm
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To assess the fate of patients who have undergone a technical procedure at the Cardiology
      Plate (implantation / extraction of a pacemaker, a defibrillator, radiofrequency ablation or
      cryo-ablation, left auricle closure, electro- Physiological exploration), and to determine
      prognostic factors / markers in this population.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
